<div class="tashuo-single J-item" data-tashuoId="9e811c1412ad9a312b92e507">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/tashuo/authorcenter?authorId=013e9d8661f990966c2a1a20" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/2fdda3cc7cd98d104e4b182a2b3fb80e7bec9009.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>张天翼</strong>
<span>影评人</span>
</div>
